@{b}      BBS Status Info@{ub}
@{b}      ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

                Name: The name of your BBS
                      ( max.19 characters; BBSNAME-Tooltype )

          /X Version: The versionnumber of AmiExpress
                      ( max. 6 characters )

            Location: The location of your BBS
                      ( max.19 characters; BBSLOCATION-Tooltype )

              # HD's: The number of HD's you use for your BBS
                      ( max.2 characters; HDCOUNT-Tooltype )

        Type of HD's: The type of Harddiskdrive(s) you use for your BBS
                      ( max.19 characters; HDTYPE-Tooltype )

       Free HD Space: The free Harddiskdrive(s) space for uploads
                      ( max.13 characters )

               Sysop: The Name/Handle of the Sysop
                      ( max.19 characters )

           Chat Mode: ON/OFF ... shows if Sysop is available for chat on the
                      current node
                      ( max.3 characters )

         Total Confs: The total number of conferences
                      ( max.3 characters )

         Total Nodes: The total number of nodes
                      ( max.3 characters; NODES-Tooltype )

        Active Nodes: The number of active Nodes
                      ( max.3 characters )

      Inactive Nodes: The number of inactive Nodes
                      ( max.3 characters )


@{b}      User Status Info@{ub}
@{b}      ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

         Name/Handle: The name/handle of the user
                      ( max.18 characters )

         Area Access: The area to which the user belongs to
                      ( max.18 characters )

      Location/Group: The location/group the user belongs to
                      ( max.18 characters )

        Phone Number: The phonenumber of the user
                      ( max.18 characters )

       Computer Type: The number of the Computer the user uses
                      ( see ComputerList-Icon for complete )
                      ( max.3 characters )

         Accesslevel: The accesslevel of the user
                      ( max.3 characters )

        Current Slot: The current slot the user uses
                      ( max.3 characters )

        Current Node: The current node on which the user logged in
                      ( max.3 characters )

        Current Conf: The current joined conference of the user
                      ( max.18 characters )

      Current Conf #: The current joined conference number of the user
                      ( max.3 characters )

         Expert Mode: ON/OFF... shows the mode of the user...
                      menue display ON or menue display OFF
                      ( max.3 characters )

       Current Ratio: The ratio of the user
                      ( max.1 character )

          Ratio Type: The ratio type of the user
                      ( max.9 characters )

             Uploads: The number of files the user uploaded in the current conference
                      ( max.19 characters )

      Uploaded Bytes: The number of bytes the user uploaded in the current conference
                      ( max.19 characters )

           Downloads: The number of files the user downloaded in the current conference
                      ( max.19 characters )

       Leeched Bytes: The number of bytes the user downloaded in the current conference
                      ( max.19 characters )

       Today Leeched: The number of bytes the user downloaded in the current conference
                      today
                      ( max.19 characters )

          Byte Limit: The number of bytes the user may download
                      ( max.18 characters )

          Time Limit: How many minutes the user may use the BBS today
                      ( max.5 characters )

        Msg's Posted: The number of messages the user has written
                      in the current conference
                      ( max.18 characters )

         Line Length: How many lines are displayed in output
                      ( max.3 characters )

               Calls: The number of total calls the user has made
                      ( max.18 characters )

   Last Call/Last On: The date and time of user's last call
                      ( max.25 characters )

    Time used/Online: How many minutes the user has used the BBS already
                      ( max.5 characters )

   Total Time/Online: How many minutes the user may use the BBS at total
                      ( max.5 characters )

   Connect Baud/Baud: The Baudrate of the user with that he connected to
                      the BBS
                      ( max.6 characters )


@ENDNODE

